data.description: Home just appraised at $315,000. Buyer had to back out of deal. Lucky you. New roof w/ warranty, Septic pumped & certified, New 65x12 porch & exterior two-tone paint. Beautiful refinished stucco exterior w/ window moldings, newer dual pane windows, new front door, newer RUUD a/c unit & furnace. Bedrooms retextured New paint,doors & vinyl plank flooring & Sub flooring. Both Bathrooms have new showers, toilets, sinks & vinyl plank flooring. Come see all this peaceful 4.17 acre horse property has to offer.
